73
00:04:07,317 --> 00:04:08,437
Peut-être.

74
00:04:21,101 --> 00:04:22,798
T'as regardé !

75
00:04:23,579 --> 00:04:24,851
Tu sais !

76
00:04:25,133 --> 00:04:26,870
Tu sais quand je vais mourir !

77
00:04:27,010 --> 00:04:28,027
